Preheat your #oven{} to 220°C/200°C fan/gas mark 7. Bring a large #saucepan{} of
water to the boil with @salt{1/2%tsp} for the pasta.

Halve the @baby plum tomatoes{125%g}.

Peel and grate the @garlic clove{2} (or use a #garlic press{}).

== Roasted Tomatoes ==

Pop the tomatoes onto a piece of foil.

Drizzle over some @olive oil{}. Season with @salt{}, @ground black pepper{} and
the @sugar{1/2%tsp}.

Fold the foil, sealing on all sides to create a parcel, then place onto a
small #baking tray{}.

When the oven is hot, roast the tomatoes on the top shelf until softened,
~{12-15%mins}.

== Pasta and Bacon ==

Meanwhile, add the @rigatoni pasta{180%g} to the boiling water and bring back
to the boil.

Cook until tender, ~{12%mins}.

While the pasta cooks, heat a drizzle of @olive oil{} in a large #frying pan{}
on medium heat.

Once hot, add the @British smoked bacon lardons{90%g} and stir-fry until
golden, ~{4-5%mins}.

> IMPORTANT: Wash your hands and equipment after handling raw meat. Cook bacon
> thoroughly.

== Creamy Sauce ==

Once the bacon is golden, stir in the garlic and cook for ~{1%min}.

Stir in the @water{150%ml} and @vegetable stock paste{10%g}. Bring to the boil,
then simmer until slightly reduced, ~{1-2%mins}.

Once reduced, stir in the @creme fraiche{150%g}, bring back to the boil, then
remove from the heat. Taste and add salt and pepper if needed.

== Assembly ==

Once cooked, drain the pasta in a #colander{}, then add to the pan of creamy
sauce along with the @peas{120%g} and heat through for ~{1-2%mins}.

Add the @baby spinach{40%g} to the pan a handful at a time until wilted and
piping hot, ~{1-2%mins}.

Stir through the @grated hard Italian style cheese{20%g}, then taste and season
with salt and pepper if needed. Add a splash of water if you feel it needs it.

== To Serve ==

When everything's piping hot, spoon the bacon pesto pasta into your bowls and
drizzle over the @fresh pesto{32%g}.

Carefully remove your roasted tomatoes from the foil and serve them on top.

Spoon over the tomato juices from the parcel to finish.

Enjoy!